song.title: Aivoryy
song.info:
Norwegian lyrics: "Vi kan'ke kode eller lage musikk, grafikken blir jo rævva, men det driter vi i for vi er Ivory. Åå-å-åååh for vi er Ivory! Hei!
Vi kan'ke kode eller lage musikk, grafikken blir jo rævva, men det driter vi i for vi er Ivory. Åå-å-åååh for vi er Ivory! Hei!
*Sniff sniff* Her lukter det... *Sniff sniff* Ivory!"
English: "We can't code or create music, graphics are fucked up, but we don't care because we are Ivory! Oh-o-ooh because we are Ivory! Hi!
We can't code or create music, graphics are fucked up, but we don't care because we are Ivory! Oh-o-ooh because we are Ivory! Hi!
*sniff sniff* It's smelly here... *sniff sniff* Ivory!"
